{"tid":1116824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【暴雨警告】5男女出海遇大風 4人墮海2人失蹤","createTime":"2019-04-20T09:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T12:47:45.000Z","uid":52698,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"59fde307bcbf6ba935ddf43fb0d527fa5e4373bb","tid":1116824,"uid":52698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190420/large/1555750212_57af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190420%2Flarge%2F1555750212_57af.jpg&h=1c4b19b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文台先後發出黃色及紅色暴雨警告，下午3時20分黃色暴雨警告仍然生效，本港多處落大雨，而且有高達每小時100公里或以上的陣風吹襲本港，警方更接獲多個墮海求救報告。<br />\n相關新聞：【暴雨來襲】東莞多地水浸 廣州逾百班機受阻<br />\n<br />\n據了解，5名男女下午2時許乘一艘船出海，駛至藍灣半島對開，疑大風浪下4名男女墮海，而船上的另一名男子立即報警求救。救援人員趕到鯉景灣，得悉船隻被風浪吹到將軍澳工業邨對開海面擱淺，其後救援人員將其中二人救起，正搜索另外兩名失蹤人士。<br />\n此外，下午2時，龍鼓灘有漁船翻轉，3名船員由水警救起，沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190420/59510427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F59510427&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=0870f1f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F59510427&h=14abc1f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190420/59510427</a>"},{"pid":"223bba17dec8efc7b30972983b2cc6ffef12b3da","tid":1116824,"uid":161195,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f52646ac4c3160016dd38b100001009087e469f","tid":1116824,"uid":90802,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"次次打風大雨實有啲傻閪以為好型走去落水，最後要麻煩消防救護釣返班賤種上黎，好彩今次出事嘅係班撚屌姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46449bedb096536379dbfc3f7dda6e723b57acaa","tid":111